Package org.group8.view

Interface IHealthcenterGUI

All Known Implementing Classes:
HealthcenterGUI
public interface IHealthcenterGUI
The IHealthcenterGUI interface defines the methods required for the graphical user interface of the health center simulation. It provides input methods for the controller and allows interaction with visualizations of the simulation.
